5:
Looks like people in this world also
celebrate Halloween.
7:
We're finished with the delivery, so
why don't we wander around a bit?
14:
Well, that's it for today. I'm so glad I
got to see you again.
17:
It... was my pleasure! I'm h-happy I
got to see you, too.
19:
Hehe... That's a good little kitten. I'll
be waiting for you on the ship.
23: ...Yeesh. Guess I can finally go home—
31:
Don't worry, Rain. You've got our full
support, no matter what you're into!
44:
...That man from earlier is the CEO of
a company suspected of
conducting illegal transactions.
However, proof has been difficult to
find.
48:
He has a reputation of being a
womanizer of sorts, so I figured that
maybe this could work...
52:
Looks like things are going along...
smoothly? You've already got
another date planned, right?
56:
He invited me to a party on his
luxury liner. We don't have any intel
on that ship yet either, so it's
something of a golden opportunity...
60:
B-but I don't get why things are
going as well as they are!
64:
I mean, I can take a guess, but you
might not like it...
73:
...I've still not gone far enough to
climb the ranks.
79:
The ranks of what? The popularity
contest at the local maid café?
88:
I have to do whatever I can to climb
the NAVY ranks. Otherwise, I'll never
be able to help the floatdwellers!
91: Alk, Stella. Will you help me?
96:
It's wonderful to be with you again,
my little kitten.
97:
I nearly lost my mind when I saw you
bringing another man with you, but...
100:
I-I told you, did I not? The riffraff
have been too bold recently, so I
had to hire a bodyguard.
103:
Besides... I don't want to worry about
anything other than enjoying my
time with you.
110:
O-of course not! Hire as many
bodyguards as you want!
113:
Anyway... Shall we continue our
conversation from earlier?
115:
You were saying you handle the
finances at your company yourself.
That's amazing!
118:
Yes! Leaving too many secrets with
your subordinates is asking for
trouble.
120:
If I can't keep the things most
precious to me close at hand, I can't
relax. I feel the same way about you,
too...
123:
Oh... I'd... like to hear more. Under the
stars.
126:
Alone, together. We'll leave the
bodyguard behind...
129:
Hehe... You're a daring little kitten,
aren't you? I like that.
134:
The stars are beautiful tonight. I
could stare at them forever...
139:
You're more beautiful than all the
stars in the universe. Those shining
eyes, that flawless skin...
142:
S-stop it, silly... You're making me
blush...
145:
Oh? Do you not like my romantic
prose? Well, get used to me singing
your praises, my bashful little kitten...
159:
I found the ledger in his room!
They've been trading tons of illegal
merchandise!
170:
You didn't think you could run away
while at sea, did you? Hand over the
ledger...
173:
Of course we can run. When I'm with
this guy, nothing's impossible!
179:
These shoes are incredible! You're
actually running on water!
182:
Yeah! Be careful, though. We'll sink if
our balance gets thrown off!
186:
So... Grab my hand, and never let go,
you big cutie.
189:
Haha! Just kidding! Had you going
for a second, didn't I?
195: You better believe it. After all...
198:
Stella got me to read KoiAzu, and
now I know everything there is to
know about being adorable!
